metadata.name: Crazy Deer 1
metadata.description: Join a new era of creative communities with our NFT project, designed BY ARTISTS, FOR ARTISTS & ART LOVERS. Our community is built around 7777 unique deer NFTs, each serving as a keycard to unlock exclusive access to real-life concerts, exhibitions, meetups, members-only servers, and live-streams. As an NFT holder, you'll also receive daily drops of a 77 chapter story called THE CRAZY SEVEN, immersing you in a world of creativity and collaboration. Whether you're a musician, writer, painter, performing artist, CGI designer, or AI artist, you can submit any kind of art and become a creative part of our gang.
